		<item>
		<title>This Week in Review: Ferguson and press freedom, and BuzzFeed’s $50 million boost</title>
		<link>http://markcoddington.com/2014/08/21/this-week-in-review-ferguson-and-press-freedom-and-buzzfeeds-50-million-boost/</link>
		<comments>http://markcoddington.com/2014/08/21/this-week-in-review-ferguson-and-press-freedom-and-buzzfeeds-50-million-boost/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 21 Aug 2014 20:05:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Mark]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[this week]]></category>
