		<title>This Week in Review: Covering war in real time, and evaluating a pair of plagiarism cases</title>
		<link>http://markcoddington.com/2014/08/14/this-week-in-review-covering-war-in-real-time-and-evaluating-a-pair-of-plagiarism-cases/</link>
		<comments>http://markcoddington.com/2014/08/14/this-week-in-review-covering-war-in-real-time-and-evaluating-a-pair-of-plagiarism-cases/#respond</comments>
