		<item>
		<title>This Week in Review: The Fox/Time Warner dance begins, and clickbait and its discontents</title>
		<link>http://markcoddington.com/2014/07/31/this-week-in-review-the-foxtime-warner-dance-begins-and-clickbait-and-its-discontents/</link>
		<comments>http://markcoddington.com/2014/07/31/this-week-in-review-the-foxtime-warner-dance-begins-and-clickbait-and-its-discontents/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2014 19:42:30 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Mark]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[this week]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[21st Century Fox]]></category>
